"""
pso-check — PSO Automated Test Suite
Fully self-contained. Spins up its own isolated environment, runs
structural checks, functional tests against real components, and
a full CLI command sweep — then tears everything down.

No manual steps required beyond running this file.

Usage:
  ./pso-check                     Full suite (all 3 phases)
  ./pso-check --quick             Structural checks only (fast)
  ./pso-check --functional        Functional tests only
  ./pso-check --cli-only          CLI command sweep only
  ./pso-check --no-cleanup        Keep test environment after run
"""

